dcterms:description: A dataset containing extensive information about different statistical and empirical features for 124 LiFePO4 batteries tested from maximum capacity until they reached 80 percent of the initial charge/discharge capacity. It includes data such as temperature, internal resistance, discharge capacity, charge capacity, and several other measurable data points.
dcterms:title: LiFePO4 Battery Cycle Life Dataset
